OL,3,CCritical infrastructure hit as risk of
OL,4,Cenergy shock rises
OL,6,FToday, the targeting of energy
OL,7,Finfrastructure intensified. Strikes
OL,8,Fhave reportedly hit key sites
OL,9,Fincluding Iran's South Pars gas field
OL,10,F- one of the world's largest - and Ras
OL,11,FLaffan, Qatar's main liquefied natural
OL,12,Fgas export hub.
OL,14,FAlongside ports, pipelines,
OL,15,Frefineries, and storage facilities,
OL,16,Fthese are critical arteries in the
OL,17,Fglobal energy system. Damage here
OL,18,Frisks turning disruption into a
OL,19,Fprolonged supply shock.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
