OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1773943560
OL,3,CCritical infrastructure hit as risk of
OL,4,Cenergy shock rises
OL,6,FPrices are already moving higher.
OL,7,FBrent crude is now around $110 a
OL,8,Fbarrel - roughly 50% above pre-war
OL,9,Flevels. That is enough to push up
OL,10,Finflation and increase pressure on
OL,11,Fcentral banks, even if it remains
OL,12,Fbelow the peaks seen in past crises.
OL,14,FAt the centre of it all is the Strait
OL,15,Fof Hormuz. Satellite data shows very
OL,16,Flittle traffic moving through the
OL,17,Fchannel. Only a handful of vessels
OL,18,Fpassed through yesterday, mostly
OL,19,Fheading towards India, Pakistan, and
OL,20,FChina.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1773943560
OL,3,CCritical infrastructure hit as risk of
OL,4,Cenergy shock rises
OL,6,FFor now, Iran appears to be
OL,7,Fcontrolling what goes in and what
OL,8,Fcomes out.
OL,10,FThe result is simple: large amounts of
OL,11,Foil and gas are not reaching the
OL,12,Fplaces where they are in demand. If
OL,13,Fthat continues, the adjustment will
OL,14,Fnot come from increased supply, but
OL,15,Ffrom reduced demand - in other words,
OL,16,Fthe world will have to consume less.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
