OL,3,CCritical infrastructure hit as risk of
OL,4,Cenergy shock rises
OL,6,FDonald Trump is trying to reopen the
OL,7,FStrait but has not succeeded so far.
OL,8,FMeanwhile, petrol prices in the United
OL,9,FStates are rising, and with them,
OL,10,Fpolitical pressure.
OL,12,FBecause if recent years have shown
OL,13,Fanything, it is that voters loathe
OL,14,Finflation - and when prices rise, they
OL,15,Ftend to blame the government.
OL,17,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,18,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,19,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,20,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/7
